Before changing ghast-family lift, mesh composition, UV bake, or GPU bind behavior, read [docs/ghast-family-parity.md](../../docs/ghast-family-parity.md).

Required invariants:

- Lift terminal `LayerDefinition.apply(MeshTransformer.scaling(...))` into inherited root `uniformScale` and Mojang root Y translation.
- Monster ghast tentacles are root children; Happy Ghast tentacles are body children.
- Preserve Java tentacle cuboids as local `+Y` boxes and use standard LER. Do not restore ghast-specific reflection or face-slot UV compensation.
- Bake Geometry IR UVs against manifest logical atlas dimensions, not padded physical PNG dimensions.
- Validate direct jar lift, runtime `renderPartAffines`, CPU rebake, GPU bind prep, and a real visual preview. Green unit tests alone do not sign off this family.
